  <brief_title>Effect of Cranberry Capsules on Urinary Infection Rates in Spinal Cord Injured Patients During Post Acute Rehabilitation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of the Effect of Cranberry Capsules on the Occurrence of Urinary Tract Infections During Post-acute Rehabilitation of Spinal Cord Injured Patients</official_title>
